```plantuml
@startuml Fintan-contents_case-studies

actor User
participant "Frontend (React/Redux)" as Frontend
participant "Backend (Spring Boot)" as Backend
participant "CI/CD Pipeline" as CICD
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Monitoring (New Relic)" as Monitoring
participant "Auth Service" as Auth

User -> Frontend: Accesses application
Frontend -> Auth: Request authentication
Auth --> Frontend: Authentication token
Frontend -> Backend: API request (with token)
Backend -> Auth: Validate token
Auth --> Backend: Validation response
Backend -> DB: Query data
DB --> Backend: Return data
Backend --> Frontend: API response
Frontend -> User: Render UI

group CI/CD Deployment
    CICD -> Backend: Trigger build
    Backend --> CICD: Build artifacts
    CICD -> Backend: Run tests
    Backend --> CICD: Test results
    CICD -> Backend: Deploy to production
    Backend -> Monitoring: Register deployment
end

Backend -> Monitoring: Send performance metrics
Monitoring --> Backend: Alert if anomalies

@enduml
```